Combine cranberry juice, water, SPLENDA(R) Granulated Sweetener, and KOOL-AID(R) Soft Drink Mix in a medium saucepan, stirring until SPLENDA(R) Granulated Sweetener dissolves. Add cinnamon sticks and cloves and bring to a boil. Reduce heat to low and simmer, uncovered, 15 minutes. Remove spices with a slotted spoon. Discard cloves and reserve cinnamon sticks for garnish. Garnish with cinnamon sticks and orange slices and serve immediately.